Articles.Content:
Hi,

Through I'd get KSP going in prep for KSP2.

I've not playing in some time (pre PD launcher) but I'm unable to launch the game.

Verified files and totally reinstalled with the same results.

  • The launcher opens and I can click play. 
  • The loading splash screen shows,
  • A box briefly pops up,
    • Seems to say something about unity with a picture of Jeb and a Red ! but it's gone so quickly that I can't say for sure what it's trying to tell me.
  • After that, I'm back at the desktop.

System spec

  •  Win11,
  • 32GB Ram,
  • AMD 5800X,
  • AMD 6700XT
Can you possibly post the log file?  That might have some information indicating why you are crashing.

Sorry, where would I find that log?

I can't see a folder or log files in the steam install directory

Edited February 21, 2023 by daveo132
